// Store(1) Up(1) Down(1) SW(16_Hex) _ LED(4)
// Note: Conditioners take time to settle. This TB assumes 
// we either bypassed the conditioner or wait long enough. 
// For simulation, it is often easier to force the internal "conditioned" signals 
// or reduce the conditioner constant to 1.
0 0 0 0000_0000
0 1 0 0000_0001  // Up pressed -> LED 1
0 0 0 0000_0001  // Release -> LED 1
0 1 0 0000_0010  // Up pressed -> LED 2
...